00:34:55,810 --> 00:34:58,973
Look, l even checked the names
of every government--

482
00:34:59,747 --> 00:35:02,011
l was just getting some coffee.

483
00:35:04,719 --> 00:35:07,449
l checked names of every
government employee quoted...

484
00:35:07,655 --> 00:35:11,989
...against a book listing the names of
all government employees in the U.S.

