488
00:35:23,905 --> 00:35:26,237
Stephen Glass

489
00:35:26,441 --> 00:35:28,568
David, for Chrissakes.

490
00:35:28,776 --> 00:35:30,607
Oh, God, I'm sorry, Stephen.

491
00:35:30,812 --> 00:35:35,010
