00:35:54,102 --> 00:35:55,865
Of course you did.

498
00:35:56,237 --> 00:35:59,172
Rob and Aaron would kill you
over that kind of stuff.

499
00:35:59,540 --> 00:36:02,475
This is The New Republic,
remember? Nothing slides here.

500
00:36:02,677 --> 00:36:05,339
lf you don't have it cold,
you don't turn it in, ever.

501
00:36:05,546 --> 00:36:07,104
-Okay.
-Look...

502
00:36:07,315 --> 00:36:09,783
...bring me your notes later.
We'll go through it.

503
00:36:09,984 --> 00:36:12,214
There's a lot about it that l liked.

504
00:36:12,420 --> 00:36:14,354
-Really?
-Really.

505
00:36:14,922 --> 00:36:18,153
And get back to work, okay?
The mailroom floor needs scrubbing.

506
00:36:18,359 --> 00:36:21,089
Okay. Hey, thanks, Stephen.

507
00:36:30,204 --> 00:36:33,935
