00:37:01,335 --> 00:37:02,700
it's good to stretch.

516
00:37:02,904 --> 00:37:04,462
l just....

517
00:37:05,039 --> 00:37:07,337
l don't think you're writing
to your strengths.

518
00:37:07,742 --> 00:37:09,835
-Can l...?
-l mean....

519
00:37:15,750 --> 00:37:18,844
l wonder why you'd wanna stray
from the things you do so well.

520
00:37:25,326 --> 00:37:29,592
Have you noticed the way Steve's
phone has been ringing lately?

521
00:37:29,797 --> 00:37:32,925
Did you see all those editors
at the correspondents dinner?

522
00:37:33,134 --> 00:37:36,365
-The way they were circling him?
