523
00:37:36,904 --> 00:37:40,203
To get a bunch of smoke blown
up your ass by a pack of editors?

524
00:37:40,408 --> 00:37:43,605
Yes. Yes, it is.

525
00:37:45,580 --> 00:37:47,104
Caitlin...

