529
00:37:57,758 --> 00:37:59,385
Amy...

530
00:37:59,794 --> 00:38:01,193
...you don't write funny.

531
00:38:06,167 --> 00:38:08,499
it's a little funny.

532
00:38:10,238 --> 00:38:11,466
isn't it?

533
00:38:13,274 --> 00:38:15,936
-l was just looking for Stephen.
-He's in his office.

534
00:38:24,619 --> 00:38:27,281
-You got a minute, Steve?
-Yeah.

535
00:38:27,488 --> 00:38:29,979
You have numbers for your sources
on ''Hack Heaven''?

536
00:38:30,191 --> 00:38:31,385
But they're at home.

537
00:38:31,592 --> 00:38:33,253
-Can l get them?
-Of course.

538
00:38:33,461 --> 00:38:36,055
Did l do something wrong?
Are you mad at me?

539
00:38:36,264 --> 00:38:38,858
No, l just need the phone numbers.

540
00:38:41,168 --> 00:38:42,635
Okay.

541
00:38:43,971 --> 00:38:46,462
Okay. Okay, I'm trying to keep cool
about all this.

