550
00:39:16,704 --> 00:39:17,898
Do you see the irony?

551
00:39:18,105 --> 00:39:21,768
The snobbiest rag in the business,
in-flight magazine of Air Force One...

552
00:39:21,976 --> 00:39:24,536
...and their star goes
and gets completely snowed...

553
00:39:24,745 --> 00:39:26,474
...by a bunch of hackers.

