00:40:24,438 --> 00:40:25,905
Kambiz just handed it to you.

568
00:40:26,173 --> 00:40:29,370
lf l hadn't been at the dentist,
it'd be me about to get famous.

569
00:40:29,577 --> 00:40:32,569
