00:41:09,483 --> 00:41:13,283
What kind of parent goes on vacation
with their kid in early May?

579
00:41:14,155 --> 00:41:17,750
That's a good question.
l guess you have to know his mom.

580
00:41:17,958 --> 00:41:19,983
She's a little quirky.

581
00:41:20,695 --> 00:41:24,961
That's his email address
if you want to write him yourself.

582
00:41:26,300 --> 00:41:28,632
These are all my notes.

583
00:41:29,336 --> 00:41:31,736
That's for the
National Assembly of Hackers.

584
00:41:31,939 --> 00:41:36,308
Don't be thrown if all you hear is like
a dark, deep, heavy breathing. it's--

585
00:41:36,510 --> 00:41:39,138
l don't know, their outgoing
voice-mail message.

