00:42:19,487 --> 00:42:21,318
Please leave a message.

603
00:42:21,522 --> 00:42:24,685
it's Charles Lane from The New
Republic in Washington D.C.

604
00:42:24,892 --> 00:42:27,360
I'd like to speak to George Sims,
